name: Flying the Air Canada Rouge 767! Premium Rouge Orlando to Toronto
description:
Air Canada Rouge is Air Canada’s vacation brand, and at the time this was filmed, flew a fleet of A320 family aircraft and 25 Boeing 767s.

These 25 767s were sadly retired from passenger service in the spring, but I had the chance to fly one at the end of 2019.

With Rouge having recently restarted operations, I figured now was as good a time to share it as any!
